# Kiro specs: only the universal-blockchain-node-runner spec is published to the
# public repo. All other specs and the local security review docs (review-*)
# are kept local. NOTE: .gitignore does not untrack already-committed files —
# specs previously committed must also be removed from the index with
# `git rm -r --cached <path>`.
.kiro/specs/*
!.kiro/specs/universal-blockchain-node-runner/
# Kiro per-task execution metadata (session IDs, timestamps) is local IDE
# state, not project content. Re-exclude it from the otherwise-tracked spec dir.
.kiro/specs/universal-blockchain-node-runner/**/tasks.meta.json